title: All-New Holidays At Universal Orlando Resort
description: "This year Universal Orlando Resort takes the Christmas season to new heights with an all-new lineup of festivities. Experience Christmas in The Wizarding World of Harry Potter™ as Hogsmeade™ and Diagon Alley™ are transformed with wondrous spirit. Watch the live retelling of Dr. Seuss's classic holiday tale starring The Grinch™ as the Grinchmas Who-liday Spectacular returns. Merry and Mayhem combine as the Minions join Santa Claus in the all-new Universal's Holiday Parade featuring Macy's. Make it a Christmas to remember at Universal Orlando Resort."

title: Orlando Tropical Ultimate New Years Eve 2018!
description:
"DCBX, BK Fade, O-Town Social & DJ Oso Present... Orlando Tropical Ultimate New Years Eve 2018!at The Holiday Inn Hotel Universal in Orlando, FL.  "The Biggest Latin NYE in Orlando!  
10 Top International DJs - 4 Ballrooms - 2 VIP Areas - 4 Hour VIP Open Bar - 1 Rooftop VIP Event - 10+ Special Performances  - 1 Unforgettable LED Countdown 
Celebrate NYE in Style.  LED Party favors for everyone!4-hour Premium VIP OPEN BAR: This VIP experience includes a private bar, and upgraded party favors. (Limited tickets available). Must be 21+ to participate 
About the Event: 


Special Pre Party December 30th 

Featuring 3x current Bachata Cabaret and Salsa Finalist from Cuba and Canada Harold and Regan.  

9:30pm-1:30am Premier Open Bar for VIPs (4 Hours)


10pm Renowned Latin Dance Shows with International Professionals 


Midnight - Champagne toast & Midnight Surprise Show!


Special Room Rate $124/night if reserved by Dec. 9th. 

Complimentary Champagne Toast at Midnight!
